"{\"uid\": \"thefederalist.com-2024-08-01-why-non-christians-should-care-about-the-olympics-drag-show\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The drag spectacle creates doubt about some cherished assumptions of the modern secular world.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 94, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The drag spectacle\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 27, \"to\": 32}, {\"ngram\": \"some cherished assumptions\", \"from\": 39, \"to\": 65}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern secular world\", \"from\": 69, \"to\": 93}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremonies of the Paris Olympics were deeply offensive to Christians around the world.\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9648419206141904, \"rank\": 0.036436950570867314, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Numerous people from across the denominational spectrum have described this event as blasphemous and even demonic.\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Numerous people\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 210}, {\"ngram\": \"the denominational spectrum\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 276}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, I would like to say something to the non-Christians who may be uneasy about the opening ceremonies but cannot quite explain why.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"the non\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"Christians\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps the opening ceremony bothers you, but you are not quite ready to align yourself with its Christian critics.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9974901461639731, \"rank\": 0.0025161690524046, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let me help you with this.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The group of people who created this spectacle betrayed the trust that was placed in them.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The group\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"this spectacle\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the trust\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were given responsibility for an event that should have honored the athletes and the pursuit of excellence.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 714}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"the pursuit\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, they used it to put themselves and their agenda at the center of attention.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their agenda\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And their conduct creates doubt about some cherished assumptions of the modern secular world.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their conduct\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"some cherished assumptions\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 946}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern secular world\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us start by giving a moment's thought to the athletes.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment's thought\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These world-class athletes have spent years preparing for the opportunity to compete in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These world-class athletes\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes deserve to be honored for their dedication and pursuit of excellence.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"their dedication\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"pursuit\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, these men and women who are talented and self-disciplined were upstaged by men and women who are neither.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these men\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"neither\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not need to be a Christian to see that something is seriously wrong with this picture.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1361, \"end\": 1370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9974901461639731, \"rank\": 0.0025161690524046, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"this picture\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have all been told that we are supposed to tolerate and even honor the type of people who created this spectacle.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the type\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"this spectacle\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gay people are oppressed victims, after all.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gay people\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"oppressed victims\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were born this way, after all.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is nothing wrong with being gay, after all.\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we agree that pathological self-centeredness is not \\\"virtually normal?\\\"\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pathological self-centeredness\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suppose we agree, for the sake of argument, that people are \\\"born gay,\\\" (a point I by no means concede).\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sake\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"argument\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"gay\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"no means concede\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we at least agree that wearing garish costumes is not an inborn, immutable trait?\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"garish costumes\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"an inborn, immutable trait\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we agree that having an irresistible urge to ridicule other people's beliefs is not generally a sign of good mental health?\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an irresistible urge\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"other people's beliefs\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"a sign\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"good mental health\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if we agree that people do not \\\"choose to be gay,\\\" can we agree that these individuals did chose to put on this particularly tasteless display in a wildly inappropriate time and place?\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"these individuals\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"this particularly tasteless display\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"a wildly inappropriate time\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They did not make \\\"a choice\\\": They made hundreds of choices over the course of many years that led them to believe what they did was a fine thing to do.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"a choice\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"choices\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"a fine thing\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The artistic \\\"genius\\\" who created this event claimed he wanted to be \\\"inclusive.\\\"\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The artistic \\\"genius\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He expects us to take this claim at face value.\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"this claim\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"face value\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is either delusional about the effects his work would have, or he is lying through his teeth.\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the effects\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"his work\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"his teeth\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knew perfectly well he would offend and disgust many people.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had to have known that even among the people who were not offended for religious reasons, a sizeable number would be bored, turn off their TV, and stop watching the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"religious reasons\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"a sizeable number\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2822}, {\"ngram\": \"their TV\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Various individuals and entities associated with the Paris Olympics have issued statements with varying degrees of \\\"explanation\\\" and \\\"apology.\\\"\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Various individuals\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"entities\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2958}, {\"ngram\": \"statements\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"varying degrees\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"explanation\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"apology\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not going to attempt to catalogue them.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not interested, and I will tell you why.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their apologies are phony.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their apologies\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These people are not the slightest bit sorry for offending 2.4 billion Christians around the world.\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3224, \"end\": 3234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9648419206141904, \"rank\": 0.036436950570867314, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These people\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are not sorry for hogging the stage and detracting from people of authentic achievement.\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3293}, {\"ngram\": \"detracting\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3308}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3320}, {\"ngram\": \"authentic achievement\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are sorry they got caught.\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They'd do the same again if they thought they could get away with it.\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They feel entitled to do what they want for their own purposes.\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their own purposes\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have a vision for society.\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a vision\", \"from\": 3524, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They believe they are entitled to offend and marginalize the people who stand in their way.\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, it is an interesting question to ask: who is the relevant \\\"they\\\" here?\", \"from\": 3639, \"to\": 3714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interesting question\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3673}, {\"ngram\": \"the relevant \\\"they\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3707}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I make no claim to know exactly who is responsible for the opening ceremonies.\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no claim\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly who\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3750}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 3770, \"to\": 3792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But someone chose this particular gay man to be in charge.\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3798, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"this particular gay man\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3835}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone approved the end product.\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Someone\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3860}, {\"ngram\": \"the end product\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Someone is issuing these \\\"apologies\\\" and \\\"explanations.\\\"\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Someone\", \"from\": 3887, \"to\": 3894}, {\"ngram\": \"these \\\"apologies\", \"from\": 3906, \"to\": 3922}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"explanations\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know who these people are.\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these people\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we can make a general statement without fear of contradiction.\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 4046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a general statement\", \"from\": 3996, \"to\": 4015}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 4024, \"to\": 4028}, {\"ngram\": \"contradiction\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whoever they are, they have the sanction of some very powerful people: the International Olympic Committee, corporate advertisers, and no doubt, the government of France.\", \"from\": 4048, \"to\": 4218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4123, \"end\": 4154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olymp